The four bots split up, Mist flying up and the rest of the Eletors spreading 
out. They were much smaller than the gestalt, and the shots that he was 
firing were easy to avoid. They all returned fire after taking some minor 
hits. Mist fired three charges down at Abominus's head, Aqua two explosive 
spears at Abominus's abdomen, Rubble two missiles at his chest, and Cinder 
three plasma shots at the gestalt's optics. Mist saw Galaxor slashing a 
sword down at Abominus's head from behind and backed up in case something 
exploded.
